channel.description:
Some of these I worked hard on, some were for fun.
Um this is called "The thing" It was for fun.
[IMG]http://i208.photobucket.com/albums/bb32/shamfisher/thething.png[/img]
Never came up with a name for this one.I think it was my first one. [IMG]http://i208.photobucket.com/albums/bb32/shamfisher/newgmaeframe.png[/img]
Twin swords frame, I did it for a contest months ago, think it was my second. [IMG]http://i208.photobucket.com/albums/bb32/shamfisher/gameframealmostdone.png[/img]
[u][b]The Plasma Tech Series[/b][/u] EDIT: They are Different colors because on the first forums i posted them on ppl wanted re-colors. And the silver and black one is actually the last one i made of them, i also didn't just recolor it, it has slightly different lighting effects, same for the blue-silverish one.lol
[IMG]http://i208.photobucket.com/albums/bb32/shamfisher/grey.png[/img]
Green [IMG]http://i208.photobucket.com/albums/bb32/shamfisher/greenplasmatech.png[/img]
